==Google community==
  +
'''Google Community''' (also known informally as '''GC''') is an [[Internet forum]] for discussing Google and its services, founded on [[May 1]], [[2004]] by Elliot Lee. The forum has over 35,000 articles and 3,000 registered users. The most users ever online numbered 617 on [[February 27]], [[2005]].
